<subSubSection id="9FF56510DE365168FF1890BBFD369099" pageId="10" pageNumber="183" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="D750369BDE365168FF1890BBFD369099" blockId="10.[151,1127,634,755]" pageId="10" pageNumber="183">
<emphasis id="E59BEA89DE365168FF1890BBFEDB90D8" bold="true" box="[151,281,666,690]" pageId="10" pageNumber="183">Comments.</emphasis>
The species is characterized by its very short fourth antennomere in combination with a long fifth antennomere, the sutural striae of the elytra extended along the base, and the exposed abdominal ventrites with striate microsculpture.
</paragraph>
